{"tid":1516098,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［前線教師提提你］開學家長須知","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:09:59.000Z","uid":232634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc515efae687994790f5a3cee377d16046e4fa2a","tid":1516098,"uid":232634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:19:28.000Z","msg":"學校入面最悪的學生，就係做咩都有家長撐的學生。<br />\n<br />\n學生最驚的不是被老師鬧，也不是記過，而是記過後回到家裡，父母的責罰。<br />\n<br />\n令老師最頭痛的，就是那些明明犯了錯，卻得到家長包庇和縱容的學生。面對這些學生，老師也是無可奈何。<br />\n<br />\n近日社會有聲音要求校方嚴厲處分欺凌同學的學生，或許會嚇怕部分老師和同學。所以家長們請記住，要令學生上學時「無後顧之憂」，請你<span style=\"color: purple;\">不要</span>對子女說：<br />\n<br />\n「如果你想對身邊「某d」同學做一d野，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放膽去做，爸爸媽媽一定會撐你！</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">ps 唔好同我講道德，而家打緊仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"49cee7497a9110d5f2ad9b051f006f18e3101eab","tid":1516098,"uid":27243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"係咪有把大人聲打去，就係爸爸媽媽<br />\n你知，中學啲校敄處無跟得咁實<br />\n轉咗電話又無改"},{"pid":"2c86acd5ab5554246ebad5055e6885ef4a9f6ea5","tid":1516098,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"弱弱地問一句 學校校長係咪可以無條件踢人出校？"},{"pid":"5954d5d928b6040330ce870a3e090bdc8f53c596","tid":1516098,"uid":232634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cee7497a9110d5f2ad9b051f006f18e3101eab","tid":1516098,"uid":27243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"係咪有把大人聲打去，就係爸爸媽媽<br />\n你知，中學啲校敄處無跟得咁實<br />\n轉咗電話又無改"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"學校不時都會收到電話打黎扮家長，要幫某某學生請假（其實係逃學去玩），尤其係band 3學校，校務處會有所提防的。"},{"pid":"92b85b77f47505649cd95a6f60fee0f5413be7a8","tid":1516098,"uid":232634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c86acd5ab5554246ebad5055e6885ef4a9f6ea5","tid":1516098,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"弱弱地問一句 學校校長係咪可以無條件踢人出校？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"名校要求嚴格d，踢出校自然易d。<br />\n其他學校一般要成績好差或行為問題好嚴重，再過校監個關同通報教育局。<br />\n咁易踢到人出校就好囉，老師唔洗咁辛苦。"},{"pid":"3ae54f638f3dff7c10e754a6a48d134fa1a0d35b","tid":1516098,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"毋忘聽日830香港重光紀念日。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>830中環見<br />\n830中環見<br />\n830中環見</em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96PXdYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96PXdYs.jpg&h=2d869ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KF8LYC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KF8LYC.gif&h=64c0bd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［行動Post］ 830 感謝勇武暨重光紀念日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"323ed6b02ed2f9ee2c5bddbaea3de9038cead1c2","tid":1516098,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92b85b77f47505649cd95a6f60fee0f5413be7a8","tid":1516098,"uid":232634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c86acd5ab5554246ebad5055e6885ef4a9f6ea5","tid":1516098,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"弱弱地問一句 學校校長係咪可以無條件踢人出校？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"名校要求嚴格d，踢出校自然易d。<br />\n其他學校一般要成績好差或行為問題好嚴重，再過校監個關同通報教育局。<br />\n咁易踢到人出校就好囉，老師唔洗咁辛苦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"明白"},{"pid":"01c3ace238bc87672f6344324fee4a4daefe9e6c","tid":1516098,"uid":264697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"74b4e9fd926182401cf03b330d42ba92e2112d8a","tid":1516098,"uid":232634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"推到多d家長睇到"},{"pid":"3d84905b95a96de03b